name: AnnexCore
overview: AnnexCore - An Orange County California SEO agency that helps customers compete online, and conquer the online space through search engine optimization, websites, web application, social media management, and email marketing. An established firm for nearly 4 years with experts in all fields from SEO, email marketing, google analytics, web development (PHP, Python, Magento, Drupal, and Wordpress), and social media management (facebook, twitter, linkedin, and pinterest).
